Usage: addSdpObject [-help] {[-obstruct {group(s)} ] | [-emptyRow <instName> [-numRow <val>]]}

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-emptyRow <instName>     # Empty row(s) will be inserted before/after specified
                         # instance based on the group justifyBy constraint
                         # (string, optional)
-numRow <val>            # number of row to be inserted (int, optional)
-obstruct {group(s)}     # Sdp group list (string, optional)